flowchart TB
    client([Client / curl / Ingress])

    subgraph writepath[Write path - source of truth]
        app[application-service<br/>Spring Boot 21]
        pg[(PostgreSQL<br/>Flyway migrations)]
        app -->|owns, only writer| pg
    end

    client -->|REST| app

    app -->|publish| k{{Kafka<br/>application-created<br/>application-status-updated<br/>application-deleted}}

    subgraph readpath[Event-driven consumers - database per service]
        notif[notification-service<br/>reminder scheduler]
        analytics[analytics-service<br/>reporting API]
        redis[(Redis<br/>aggregates)]
        analytics --> redis
    end

    k -->|consume| notif
    k -->|consume| analytics

    client -->|GET reminders| notif
    client -->|GET analytics| analytics

    subgraph obs[Observability - LGTM]
        otel[OTel Collector]
        prom[Prometheus]
        tempo[Tempo - traces]
        loki[Loki - logs]
        graf[Grafana]
    end

    app -. OTLP traces .-> otel
    notif -. OTLP traces .-> otel
    analytics -. OTLP traces .-> otel
    otel --> tempo
    prom -->|scrape /actuator/prometheus| app
    prom --> notif
    prom --> analytics
    graf --> prom
    graf --> tempo
    graf --> loki

    subgraph platform[Platform - GitOps]
        gha[GitHub Actions CI/CD]
        argo[ArgoCD]
        eks[AWS EKS - Terraform]
        gha -->|push images + bump tags| argo
        argo -->|sync| eks
    end
